		<div id="article" class="HOWTO-ARTICLES">
		
		<h1>Apple Portables: Calibrating your computer's battery for best performance</h1>
		<div class="padtop15"></div>
		
		
		
		<div class="meta">
			<div class="grid2col">
				<div class="column">
